                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Origin"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Summons 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Eye of Stormy Judgment</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/d0fef83593a595b2842c4a176d189819_475172351344470799.png",
                "id": "talent35513",
                "key": "Transcendence: Baleful Omen",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Transcendence: Baleful Omen"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">Electro DMG</span>. All of your other characters gain 2 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Energy</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/63dd10d83d8db6c07cd5392fa4a20a79_4946635120236318128.png",
                "id": "talent66666",
                "key": "Secret Art: Musou Shinsetsu",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Secret Art: Musou Shinsetsu"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>(Passive) When the battle begins, this character gains <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Chakra Desiderata</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Chakra Desiderata</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">After your other characters use Elemental Bursts</span>: Gain 1 Resolve. (Max 3)</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">When the character to which this is attached uses Secret Art: Musou Shinsetsu</span>: Consume all Resolve and deal +1 DMG per Resolve.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/99c934f35991c60760d939feef6ffc6a_1123134802318123762.png",
                "id": "talent61112",
                "key": "Chakra Desiderata",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Chakra Desiderata"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Summon</span></p><p>End Phase: Deal 1 <span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">Electro DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 3</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">When this Summon is on the field</span>: Your characters' Elemental Bursts deal +1 DMG.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_4931517793086785289.png",
                "id": "talent6501",
                "key": "Eye of Stormy Judgment",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/25/35428890/75f1d2ef52221da67ee1c52ce97af966_4993763992767649059.png",
                "title": "Eye of Stormy Judgment"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Electro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 for this instance, the target is forcibly switched to the next character</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] that grants +1 DMG to the next 2 instances of Dendro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_7846092102825841763.png",
                "id": "talent31731",
                "key": "Electro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Electro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Usage(s)</span></strong></p><p>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usages </span>remaining.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Energy</span></strong></p><p>Characters must consume Energy to use their Elemental Bursts.</p><p>When characters use an Elemental Skill or a Normal Attack, they will gain 1 Energy.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_5070564296734650170.png",
                "id": "talent8074",
